Subject: [PATCH] Restore update card, remove priority flags, fix mobile bell
 layout

- Detect new Vercel deploys via main bundle hash polling (15s initial check)
- Show update prompt as a card below the header instead of a bottom toast
- Refresh on update no longer wipes localStorage unless unrecoverable
- Remove priority flag buttons; drag handle replaces inline reorder affordance
- Stack task actions below title on mobile to prevent bell/text overlap
